Package edu.chalmers.service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractResource
    Abstract class containing methods and static strings for services within the package.
    AccountResource
    Handles the account parts of the server, creation of account, update, delete, login.
    FederationResource
    Handles the Federation part of the database and the connection to it.
    PartResource
    Handles the Part specific methods for the server, getting of parts and verification of authenticity.
    RESTInit
    Initiates the RESTServices for Bean injection.
    ScoreboardResource
    Will handle scoreboard once we have implemented score.
    ShipResource
    Handles the Ship part of the database and the connection to it.
